data.description: Gorgeous, renovated, 3 BR/2.5 BA townhome with over 2,230 Sq. Ft. on a spacious lot. This move-in ready home has newly installed luxury vinyl wood plank floors, private travertine front walkway, freshly painted throughout, and much more! Large kitchen and a spacious breakfast area. Natural sunlight floods the home with oversized windows and vaulted ceilings. Master bedroom located on the first floor with 2 bedrooms upstairs and a bonus room which could also be an office or a bedroom. Come relax on your screened-in patio area or enjoy the community pool.
